From [URL="https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Marvel_Database"]Marvel Database[/URL]: [QUOTE]The Green Priestesses are one of the two castes of Saturnyne's devotees, the other being the White Priestesses. Living in the wilds outside the Starlight Citadel, the Green Priestesses act as hunters and healers and prefer to follow their Lady's teachings rather than executing her direct commands.[/QUOTE] [QUOTE]The White Priestesses are one of the two castes of Saturnyne's devotees, the other being the Green Priestesses. Living within the walls of the Starlight Citadel, the White Priestesses only leave it to execute Lady Saturnyne's will.[/QUOTE]
